    "updated_at": "2014-05-24T18:40:00Z",
    "body": "This feature has previously been rejected because it makes calling a function memory-unsafe. See https://github.com/mozilla/rust/issues/8345 and https://github.com/mozilla/rust/pull/8955.\n\nI think this should be rejected on the same grounds as #8955. I wrote http://blog.octayn.net/blog/2013/10/21/on-stack-safety/ and http://blog.octayn.net/blog/2013/10/28/more-on-stack-safety/, I should probably write an update.\n",
