    "created_at": "2014-06-05T05:58:55Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-06-05T05:58:55Z",
    "body": "It's true that having an option would in theory be orthogonal to disabling/enabling per target triple, but we feel a per-target-triple setting is the best way to go at this time.\n\nFor the iOS PR, you'd just disable segmented stacks for the iOS triple, but not for other triples.\n",
